            <thetext>Currently the described option outputs the $-Array (for all used strings) also for the source build although it is not used in this build.

This can lead to problems when using special chars like &quot;\n&quot;. Using e.g. this char in the source causes the Firefox to throw an &quot;unterminated string literal&quot; error. 
The source of this error is that this char is encapsulated in a document.write command and get interpreted as line-break which causes the source-code to break.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
